Summary: planner-timeclock: Clock in with planner-task-in-progress
Keywords: 

	* planner.texi (Using planner-timeclock.el): Add note about
	clocking in with `planner-task-in-progress' and clocking out with
	`timeclock-out' or `planner-task-done'.

	* planner-timeclock.el (planner-timeclock-in): Change to an alias
	of `planner-task-in-progress'.
	(planner-task-in-progress): New. Clock in on the current task, or
	change to it if already clocked in.
	(planner-task-done): Clock out only if clocked in.
